{
  "id": "RAW_9957641a",
  "title": "Claude Opus 4.5 夺回编程王座，超 Gemini 3 Pro 和 GPT-5.1",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&mid=2247649534&idx=1&sn=c7158068b89c872e1f4e39f2665962b6",
  "date": "2025-11-25 05:01:00",
  "author": "AI前线",
  "siteName": "AI前线",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"323\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZBjVrHIdkOnVpnZic9ZtHAulA3iahJWibu0icibIANNgoW5MHiaicJqDHj3aiaBEsznqGESNXGIhMb1sJQZgROATvuicdQw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"289\" data-imgfileid=\"100165872\" data-ratio=\"0.5581127733026467\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1738\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=503612f0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnVpnZic9ZtHAulA3iahJWibu0icibIANNgoW5MHiaicJqDHj3aiaBEsznqGESNXGIhMb1sJQZgROATvuicdQw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者 ｜ 木子、高允毅 </span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 编程之王又易主了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">昨晚，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;悄悄按下发布键，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Opus 4.5</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;直接在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">编码、Agent、电脑操作</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;等多项“硬核能力”上全面登顶评测榜，超过 GPT-5.1 和最近在聚光灯下的 Gemini 3 Pro。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前测试版（Beta 版）已上线，开发者可直接通过 Claude API 调用。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100165877\" alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.075\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=da09d700&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnVpnZic9ZtHAulA3iahJWibu0Zr89gibetPH7hMwEy09gaUiaLIEkRUb2UfDmmoMXXMfoWUibicsFS2krJQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里面的</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">终端级编程能力（Agentic terminal coding）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;是个非常重要的指标，因为该指标体现了 AI 在真实终端（如电脑）环境中工作情况，不仅停留在文本层面；Claude Opus 4.5 也斩获第一，突破 59% 。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，它还在两小时限时考试里，把“史上最强人类候选者”甩在身后——而且据 Anthropic 首席产品官介绍，用的 token 数量还不到上一代的一半。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100165873\" alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1683417085427135\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"796\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8398a4ab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnVpnZic9ZtHAulA3iahJWibu09ibPjFf6q6xuag6jOmMUkOIiacJF9RxlUNfvsyp5XeribcqaeUTLhaQpw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">每百万 token 的最新定价为：5 美元 /25 美元（输入 / 输出）；批量&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">API 调用的价格更是打了 3 折左右。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100165875\" alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.774074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=49646184&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnVpnZic9ZtHAulA3iahJWibu0hjgic3iaTsENRSe9kib96XlQia7ERF1VQ1td9I0a06Uz1Tmw2bM2gsoGkQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude 老用户、一家&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 辅助编码初创公司的 CEO 表示，Opu 系列这波降价来得正好。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100165874\" alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1435768261964736\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"794\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2cf1b91e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnVpnZic9ZtHAulA3iahJWibu0Y5DRhGiaCib2pLFtEc8V1WAulR8SOwyO07XXReEqD2zRcJuW0ib6DUDvw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有网友放出一张 Meme 图，锐评这几家大模型的高速宣发节奏。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100165876\" alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9517374517374517\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1036\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=88440ad9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnVpnZic9ZtHAulA3iahJWibu0PsFWkibRiaouHYPKattjIsktc6zy0b20kSAK9rAnTN9TKa9wHxNgm6JA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251125080734_ca0a3deb&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">新一代 Claude 的 Agent 有多强？</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Opus 4.5</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">编码、Agent、计算机操作</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">等方面，都夺得测评榜第一；下面来看看它的</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">实际使用效果</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">如何。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在编程和系统调试方面</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，Claude Opus 4.5 能够</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">直接完成工程师级别的任务</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：它会自己找网络接口，会调试跨系统 bug，还会操作桌面应用、Excel、浏览器。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic 内部工程师在模型发布前做了大量压力测试，反馈高度一致：Opus 4.5 能处理模糊目标、能在多种方案中权衡取舍、不需要人工把步骤写死。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">测试者普遍认为 Opus 4.5 能“真正理解用户需求”，那些几周前 Sonnet 4.5 还几乎做不到的任务，现在对 Opus 4.5 来说已不再是难题。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">他们还把模型拉去做了个两小时的高压考试，这本来是给去 Anthropic 应聘性能工程师出的题目，是连许多顶尖候选人都吃不消的 take-home 作业。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果 Opus 4.5 在时间限制内拿到历史最高分，超过了所有人类候选者。它能读懂复杂代码库、拆解多系统交互，并在模糊指令下自动找出真正的 bug 来源。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然这份考试不涉及协作、沟通等软技能，但在纯技术判断与压力下的问题解决能力上，模型首次把“专业工程师”的门槛推向了一个全新位置。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">而且 Opus 4.5 编写的代码质量更高，在 SWE-bench Multilingual 的 8 种编程语言中，有 7 种语言的性能比领先。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100165881\" alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.549074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7d68fab0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnVpnZic9ZtHAulA3iahJWibu0cPia7uK8huDB8o1VSHrPqf7ko255eOUlWB8ARQSoeG3a0hhVM7nHLqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">复杂业务决策与工具链操作</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，比如在τ2-bench 的航空客服场景中，基础经济舱不能改签是硬规定，普通模型都会直接拒绝。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但 Opus 4.5 懂得在规则限制下“迂回求解”——比如，航空公司拒绝给经济舱换航班，它就自己先换升舱、再换航班，两步走解决单步走不了的问题，这在 benchmark 中被算作“未预期的路径”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">长期任务稳定性</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">方面，它也远超前代。在 Vending-Bench 测试中，Opus 4.5 的多步骤任务保持能力，比 Sonnet 4.5 高出&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">29%</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，几乎不会“走着走着忘了要干什么”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100165880\" alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5564814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=279b6e40&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnVpnZic9ZtHAulA3iahJWibu0pU9WDdDagTichdvZhBrhISHWgwrkuJ0ic9ibFD6E1aKOoWzmVMTD7DpUw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在视觉处理方面</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，Claude Opus 4.5 也遥遥领先于前代模型。据公司 CTO 介绍：</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">“Claude Opus 4.5 是唯一一个能搞定我们最棘手的 3D 可视化任务的模型...... 过去需要两小时才能完成的任务，现在只需要三十分钟。”</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:20px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251125080734_ca0a3deb&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">开发者平台也同步更新</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么 Claude Opus 4.5 的 Agent 会一下子变得这么强？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型层的思考能力显著提升</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，还有一个重要因素，就是</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">平台级的高级工具调用能力（advanced tool use）升级</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">——</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型和平台协同，让 Agent 不仅能说清楚，还能办好事</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">升级之后的高级工具调用能力，也被放进了 Claude 开发者平台。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在传统 Agent 工作流里，AI 想真正承担“全能助手”的角色，其实面临三道大山——</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">工具过多、调用过重、使用过难。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对这三个痛点，Opus 4.5&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">新增了三种“高级工具”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，升级之后的高级工具调用能力，也被放进了 Claude 开发者平台：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 14px 0 0 0;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Tool Search Tool：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;让模型像搜索引擎一样按需查找工具，而无需预加载全部定义。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Programmatic Tool Calling（PTC）：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;允许 Claude 用代码（如 Python）而非单独的 API 来编排工具调用，减少上下文压力。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p style=\"padding:0;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Tool Use Examples：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;教模型正确的工具调用方式，让其“看例子就会用”。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">简言之，未来 AI 可以像人一样</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">会选工具、会写自动化脚本、能看懂工具的正确用法</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">官方提供的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude for Excel</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;是最直观的例子。通过程序化工具调用，所有重载计算都在后台完成，Claude 只接收最终结果，实现了“大量数据不进脑，也能跑得快”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100165885\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.51875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ca7904d1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOnVpnZic9ZtHAulA3iahJWibu02rNsic24uKsHVBPrHU7m2WUf6iaB7LRuazfe0jKYyM9ZgWKDwNiacTIZA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude for Excel 的测试权限，已经扩展至所有 Max、Team 及 Enterprise 用户。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Mac 系统上使用 Control+Option+C，在 Windows 系统中使用 Control+Alt+C，即可在 Excel 中打开 Claude。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://x.com/claudeai/status/1993030546243699119\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/claudeai/status/1993030546243699119</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/news/claude-opus-4-5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.anthropic.com/news/claude-opus-4-5</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/engineering/advanced-tool-use\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.anthropic.com/engineering/advanced-tool-use</a></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Claude Opus 4.5 在编程、Agent 和电脑操作能力上超越现有顶级模型，并显著提升了工具调用和长期任务稳定性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Claude Opus 4.5 在编程、Agent 和电脑操作能力上超越现有顶级模型，并显著提升了工具调用和长期任务稳定性。",
  "summary": "文章报道了 Anthropic 发布的新一代大语言模型 Claude Opus 4.5，该模型在编码、Agent 能力和电脑操作等多项“硬核能力”评测中全面登顶，超越了 GPT-5.1 和 Gemini 3 Pro。其核心亮点包括在真实终端环境下的编程能力（Agentic terminal coding）突破 59%，并在高压编程考试中表现优于人类顶尖候选者。同时，Opus 4.5 在复杂业务决策和长期任务稳定性方面也取得显著进步，并大幅降低了 API 调用成本。模型能力的提升得益于其思考能力的增强以及平台级高级工具调用（advanced tool use）能力的升级，特别是新增的 Tool Search Tool、Programmatic Tool Calling 和 Tool Use Examples，使 AI 能更智能地选择和编排工具，极大扩展了其实用性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Claude Opus 4.5 在编程、Agent 和电脑操作方面性能卓越，超越现有顶级模型。",
      "explanation": "该模型在终端级编程、工程师级别任务处理和高压编程考试中均表现出色，代码质量高，树立了新的专业工程师 AI 门槛，并在多语言编程中领先。"
    },
    {
      "point": "模型在处理复杂业务决策和长期任务稳定性上取得显著进步。",
      "explanation": "Opus 4.5 能进行“迂回求解”以应对规则限制，并在多步骤任务中保持高稳定性，其多步骤任务保持能力比前代提升 29%，减少“遗忘”现象。"
    },
    {
      "point": "结合平台级高级工具调用能力，显著提升了 Agent 的实用性。",
      "explanation": "新增的 Tool Search Tool、Programmatic Tool Calling 和 Tool Use Examples 使 AI 能像人一样会选工具、写自动化脚本和理解工具用法，极大地扩展了其应用场景和效率。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Anthropic 悄悄按下发布键，Claude Opus 4.5 直接在编码、Agent、电脑操作等多项\"硬核能力\"上全面登顶评测榜，超过 GPT-5.1 和最近在聚光灯下的 Gemini 3 Pro。",
    "终端级编程能力（Agentic terminal coding）是个非常重要的指标，因为该指标体现了 AI 在真实终端（如电脑）环境中工作情况，不仅停留在文本层面；Claude Opus 4.5 也斩获第一，突破 59% 。",
    "Opus 4.5 能处理模糊目标、能在多种方案中权衡取舍、不需要人工把步骤写死。",
    "模型层的思考能力显著提升，还有一个重要因素，就是平台级的高级工具调用能力（advanced tool use）升级------模型和平台协同，让 Agent 不仅能说清楚，还能办好事。",
    "未来 AI 可以像人一样会选工具、会写自动化脚本、能看懂工具的正确用法。"
  ],
